WEBVTT

01:40.580 --> 01:45.950
[Speed and Love]

01:46.310 --> 01:48.910
[Episode 15]

02:02.350 --> 02:03.680
You've had too much to drink.

02:03.680 --> 02:04.350
No.

02:05.040 --> 02:06.270
I'm perfectly sober.

02:13.390 --> 02:14.880
The foundation course is over.

02:14.880 --> 02:15.510
Tell me,

02:16.570 --> 02:18.300
which school should I apply to?

02:29.950 --> 02:32.150
You should discuss it with your mother.

02:32.790 --> 02:34.590
She doesn't want me to stay here.

02:36.070 --> 02:37.760
She wants me to go to Canada

02:38.460 --> 02:39.710
to live with her.

02:47.110 --> 02:47.790
Jin Zhao.

02:50.040 --> 02:51.040
If I leave,

02:51.400 --> 02:53.730
I won't be able
to come back for a long time.

02:56.670 --> 02:58.070
Will you miss me?

03:37.260 --> 03:40.110
♪ Faded light that pulls me far ♪

03:42.780 --> 03:46.060
♪ Chase the whispers where you are ♪

03:48.380 --> 03:51.579
♪ Through the echoing that still string ♪

03:53.930 --> 03:57.060
♪ Every step takes me away ♪

03:58.120 --> 04:03.630
♪ Away from the noise,
the endless fights ♪

03:58.960 --> 04:00.290
You're out of your mind.

04:04.590 --> 04:08.710
♪  Through the quiet of your light ♪

04:09.760 --> 04:15.090
♪ I'll break the chains
and leave the gray ♪

04:15.780 --> 04:21.589
♪ Take me far, just take me away ♪

04:24.430 --> 04:28.100
♪ Wind is howling and calling me ♪

04:26.550 --> 04:27.810
I'm out of my mind, too.

04:29.260 --> 04:33.590
♪ Through the forest to the sea ♪

04:35.310 --> 04:39.560
♪ Shadows dance, the sky's turned grey ♪

04:40.860 --> 04:44.600
♪ But your voice still leads my ♪

04:46.500 --> 04:52.010
♪ Away from the noise,
the endless fights ♪

04:52.960 --> 04:57.080
♪  Through the quiet of your light ♪

04:58.130 --> 05:03.460
♪ I'll break the chains of life's gray ♪

05:04.150 --> 05:09.960
♪ Take me far, just take me away ♪

05:27.190 --> 05:28.110
Jiang Mu!

05:28.330 --> 05:30.500
The chicken wings are ready.
Where are you?

05:30.500 --> 05:32.500
Brandy, are you done with your call?

05:33.340 --> 05:34.140
-Master.
-Mu!

05:34.159 --> 05:35.040
Jiang Mu!

05:43.600 --> 05:44.990
Hurry, they're getting cold!

05:44.990 --> 05:45.750
Master!

05:46.280 --> 05:47.080
Brandy!

05:52.620 --> 05:54.220
What's wrong with your eyes?

05:56.280 --> 05:58.010
Brandy, what's wrong with you?

05:58.810 --> 05:59.750
We're having such a nice gathering,

05:59.750 --> 06:01.950
yet you scolded her?
She's even crying.

06:05.870 --> 06:07.070
What's your problem?

06:07.470 --> 06:08.300
Here, Jiang Mu,

06:08.300 --> 06:10.430
I grilled these chicken wings for you.

06:11.290 --> 06:12.190
Ignore him in the future.

06:12.190 --> 06:13.720
He just likes to pick on you.

06:15.160 --> 06:16.750
Stop changing the subject.

06:16.780 --> 06:18.290
You still owe me a beer.

06:18.710 --> 06:20.410
Impossible! How could I?

06:20.430 --> 06:22.080
You guys be my witnesses.
Do I owe?

06:22.080 --> 06:22.750
Two beers.

06:23.310 --> 06:25.080
I absolutely don't owe you any beers,
I'm telling you.

06:25.080 --> 06:25.960
There's no way.

06:26.250 --> 06:26.920
I'm telling you...

06:26.920 --> 06:27.870
Oh, right, Brandy,

06:27.870 --> 06:29.160
we were just thinking,

06:29.310 --> 06:30.520
in a few days when the weather clears up,

06:30.520 --> 06:31.550
let's go hiking.

06:31.640 --> 06:33.370
Let's find one with a cable car.

06:33.750 --> 06:35.810
Master, come with us. What do you say?

06:36.310 --> 06:36.870
Sure.

06:39.430 --> 06:40.190
Jiang Mu?

06:42.210 --> 06:42.850
Jiang Mu?

06:44.180 --> 06:44.780
Join us?

06:51.500 --> 06:54.030
You successfully
changed the subject again.

06:54.060 --> 06:55.460
Fate. Romance in the air.

07:11.400 --> 07:12.000
Crazy Jin,

07:12.160 --> 07:13.690
why are we gathering today?

07:14.050 --> 07:16.380
Well, Brandy emerged third in the ring...

07:21.770 --> 07:23.030
Top three in drinking.

07:23.870 --> 07:26.180
-Let's drink.
-What are you talking about?

07:26.180 --> 07:28.240
Kid, don't meddle in adult business.

07:41.340 --> 07:42.550
-Go on.
-Go on.

07:42.790 --> 07:43.880
No cheating this time!

07:43.880 --> 07:44.630
Mu,

07:45.480 --> 07:46.550
what's wrong?

07:46.800 --> 07:48.860
Are you drunk? Why is your face so red?

07:57.600 --> 07:59.110
15, 20, 15.

07:59.230 --> 08:00.740
-15, 20, 20.
-Have some water.

08:00.740 --> 08:02.220
-15, 20, 15.
-10!

08:13.660 --> 08:14.510
Do you want it?

11:40.550 --> 11:41.590
We're here.

11:54.830 --> 11:55.950
You drank today.

11:58.310 --> 12:00.510
Let's talk when you're sober tomorrow.

12:01.160 --> 12:02.470
Are you leaving?

12:11.310 --> 12:12.370
It's getting late.

12:13.220 --> 12:14.750
You should go home and rest.

12:19.790 --> 12:20.830
Zhao,

12:24.890 --> 12:25.700
don't go.

15:48.430 --> 15:50.890
What time is it now?
Why are they still not up?

16:05.920 --> 16:07.870
My head hurts so much.

16:23.950 --> 16:24.750
What's wrong?

16:24.940 --> 16:27.120
♪ What would I do ♪

16:25.320 --> 16:27.160
Mu, what happened?

16:27.150 --> 16:29.620
♪ If I have 45 minutes? ♪

16:28.950 --> 16:29.990
I'm okay!

16:30.180 --> 16:32.880
♪ Would I write a song? ♪

16:30.430 --> 16:31.190
I'm okay...

16:33.360 --> 16:35.510
♪ I don't think so ♪

16:37.080 --> 16:39.350
♪ What would I do ♪

16:39.400 --> 16:41.770
♪ If I have 70 seconds? ♪

16:42.470 --> 16:44.760
♪ Would I get a drink or two? ♪

16:44.060 --> 16:45.220
You drank today.

16:45.310 --> 16:47.770
♪ No, I don't think so ♪

16:47.590 --> 16:48.920
Let's talk when you're sober tomorrow.

16:48.590 --> 16:51.780
♪ I'd rather get on that bus ♪

16:50.950 --> 16:51.950
Jin Zhao

16:52.310 --> 16:55.000
♪ Find you where you are ♪

16:52.480 --> 16:53.570
must think that

16:53.590 --> 16:56.280
I did that on impulse
because I drank too much.

16:55.470 --> 16:57.720
♪ To talk about the cloud ♪

16:57.920 --> 17:00.570
♪ That looks just like a kangaroo ♪

16:59.760 --> 17:02.070
I was a bit impulsive, yes,

17:01.350 --> 17:04.319
♪ And the old man on the street ♪

17:02.690 --> 17:04.660
but I was conscious
of what I was doing.

17:04.660 --> 17:07.500
♪ Sat there with his dog ♪

17:05.750 --> 17:08.160
He told me to contact him when I'm awake.

17:07.900 --> 17:10.200
♪ Asking you if you're willing ♪

17:09.190 --> 17:10.880
What should I say?

17:10.230 --> 17:12.700
♪ To accompany me too ♪

17:19.109 --> 17:21.349
♪ Would you like that? ♪

17:22.050 --> 17:24.950
♪ Would you like that? ♪

17:38.630 --> 17:40.870
♪ What would I do? ♪

17:40.890 --> 17:43.630
♪ If I could fly up on the roof ♪

17:43.880 --> 17:45.630
♪ Would I rob a bank? ♪

17:46.040 --> 17:48.740
♪ Oh, I don't think so ♪

17:50.160 --> 17:52.490
♪ What would I do? ♪

17:52.510 --> 17:55.740
♪ If I could turn invisible ♪

17:55.760 --> 17:58.240
♪ Would I drive my favorite car? ♪

17:55.840 --> 17:56.670
I'm awake.

17:58.260 --> 18:01.000
♪ No, I don't think so ♪

17:58.920 --> 17:59.780
I'm still busy.

17:59.950 --> 18:01.350
Wait for me at the garage.

18:02.280 --> 18:05.480
♪ I'd go to the restaurant ♪

18:03.980 --> 18:04.660
Okay.

18:05.990 --> 18:08.550
♪ Steal all the fortune cookies ♪

18:09.130 --> 18:11.550
♪ Read them one by one ♪

18:11.580 --> 18:12.770
♪ Till it says ♪

18:12.790 --> 18:14.650
♪ That I could be with you ♪

18:15.000 --> 18:17.550
♪ Sneak into the flower shop ♪

18:15.800 --> 18:17.180
It must've been a tiring day.

18:17.180 --> 18:17.830
Mu!

18:18.050 --> 18:21.050
♪ Watch how they make their bouquets ♪

18:20.560 --> 18:21.880
I brought you some snacks.

18:21.210 --> 18:24.630
♪ So I could finally use ♪

18:22.230 --> 18:23.120
-You're welcome.
-Thank you, Mu.

18:23.120 --> 18:23.840
Thanks!

18:24.270 --> 18:25.070
I happen to be hungry.

18:24.770 --> 18:27.240
♪ The flowers I planted just for you ♪

18:25.840 --> 18:26.840
Back to work.

18:32.680 --> 18:34.780
♪ Would you like that? ♪

18:35.650 --> 18:37.770
♪ Would you like that? ♪

18:44.930 --> 18:47.090
♪ Would you like that? ♪

18:48.020 --> 18:50.090
♪ Would you like that? ♪

18:56.710 --> 18:57.640
I might take a bit longer.

18:57.340 --> 18:59.420
♪ Would you like that? ♪

18:57.870 --> 18:58.870
I can't leave yet.

19:00.440 --> 19:02.520
♪ Would you like that? ♪

19:08.350 --> 19:10.770
[Speeding Auto House]

19:12.600 --> 19:14.130
Take this car out tomorrow.

19:14.270 --> 19:15.950
Check what the shock absorber damping
should be set to.

19:15.950 --> 19:16.470
Okay.

19:18.120 --> 19:18.710
Mu.

19:19.180 --> 19:21.080
We're finishing work and leaving first.

19:21.080 --> 19:22.610
Are you waiting for Brandy?

19:23.970 --> 19:25.190
Alright, we're heading out first, then.

19:25.190 --> 19:26.400
-Bye-bye.
-Bye-bye.

22:06.800 --> 22:07.600
Sober now?

22:24.060 --> 22:26.060
Don't you have anything to say to me?

22:41.270 --> 22:43.930
If you think
you were being impulsive yesterday

22:46.370 --> 22:47.570
and you regret it now,

22:48.800 --> 22:49.800
it's not too late.

22:50.190 --> 22:51.430
I don't regret it at all.

22:51.430 --> 22:52.840
It was a bit impulsive—yes—

22:52.840 --> 22:55.040
and I was too confused to feel anything.

23:24.230 --> 23:24.960
Come with me.

24:10.950 --> 24:11.920
All my life,

24:15.830 --> 24:17.620
people have come and gone.

24:20.320 --> 24:22.450
I've never been serious about anyone.

24:28.270 --> 24:29.920
So once I get serious,

24:32.670 --> 24:35.670
I probably won't
give you a chance to change your mind.

24:39.070 --> 24:40.460
I won't change my mind.

24:42.350 --> 24:45.240
♪ Stars are twinkling in the sky ♪

24:45.630 --> 24:48.600
♪ Like your twinkling eyes ♪

24:48.850 --> 24:51.630
♪ Telling me ♪

24:52.920 --> 24:55.490
♪ A beautiful dream from afar ♪

24:57.520 --> 25:00.740
♪ Night is painted with neon lights ♪

25:01.250 --> 25:04.330
♪ The softly bustling street ♪

25:04.560 --> 25:08.400
♪ I paused and wandered far ♪

25:08.770 --> 25:12.440
♪ You're like a breeze ♪

25:10.560 --> 25:11.820
You're giving it to me?

25:13.230 --> 25:15.740
♪ I watch you leave ♪

25:15.990 --> 25:17.400
Do you know where this came from?

25:16.560 --> 25:19.990
♪ I wish I could hug you from the back ♪

25:20.460 --> 25:23.530
♪ Lingering in the air ♪

25:21.640 --> 25:22.900
My mother left it to me.

25:23.840 --> 25:26.990
♪ Your breath is everywhere ♪

25:28.590 --> 25:31.740
♪ Waiting, still waiting ♪

25:30.360 --> 25:31.250
You mean

25:32.050 --> 25:34.990
♪ You, weaving through my heart ♪

25:33.080 --> 25:34.400
your birth mother?

25:35.460 --> 25:39.240
♪ My thoughts of you will never cease ♪

25:38.310 --> 25:38.900
Then...

25:39.270 --> 25:43.960
♪ Waiting for your ship to arrive ♪

25:40.490 --> 25:42.010
this is the only thing

25:42.030 --> 25:43.290
your parents left you.

25:44.070 --> 25:46.750
♪ Waiting, still waiting ♪

25:46.510 --> 25:47.750
You are willing to give it to me?

25:47.230 --> 25:50.670
♪ You, chasing after the moon ♪

25:48.710 --> 25:50.510
I couldn't give it to you before.

25:51.410 --> 25:53.680
♪ Scattered across the sky ♪

25:51.750 --> 25:52.470
But now...

25:52.800 --> 25:54.360
Why is it okay now?

25:54.040 --> 25:57.180
♪ And me, here by your side ♪

25:57.730 --> 26:01.930
♪ No matter if it's clear
or rainy tonight ♪

25:58.380 --> 26:00.980
I'd have to start
with the origin of this thing.

26:01.840 --> 26:04.240
I'll tell you about it slowly
in the future.

26:06.330 --> 26:13.660
♪ I'll light it up, for you ♪

26:15.050 --> 26:17.730
♪ Waiting, still waiting ♪

26:18.220 --> 26:20.790
♪ You, weaving through my heart ♪

26:20.710 --> 26:22.160
You brought so many snacks.

26:21.880 --> 26:25.580
♪ My thoughts of you will never cease ♪

26:24.350 --> 26:25.730
It's like you're moving in.

26:25.730 --> 26:29.330
♪ Waiting for your ship to arrive ♪

26:30.040 --> 26:33.080
♪ I'm still waiting, still waiting ♪

26:33.580 --> 26:37.030
♪ You, chasing after the moon ♪

26:35.140 --> 26:35.930
Well...

26:37.760 --> 26:40.040
♪ Scattered across the sky ♪

26:38.180 --> 26:39.660
Can I stay here tonight?

26:40.390 --> 26:43.530
♪ And me, here by your side ♪

26:44.090 --> 26:48.290
♪ No matter if it's clear
or rainy tonight ♪

26:44.310 --> 26:45.310
What do you think?

26:48.270 --> 26:50.270
I think it might not be appropriate.

26:50.560 --> 26:51.400
Then why ask?

26:52.230 --> 26:53.670
But I want to stay.

26:52.800 --> 27:00.130
♪ I'll light it up, for you ♪

26:58.160 --> 27:01.080
I think I might be being a bit rebellious.

27:09.230 --> 27:10.360
It's true.

27:10.520 --> 27:13.150
The router at Dad's place is broken.

27:13.430 --> 27:15.060
I can't surf the web at home. It's boring.

27:15.060 --> 27:17.380
Just take it as I'm staying here

27:17.400 --> 27:19.230
for the Wi-Fi. How's that?

27:22.990 --> 27:24.720
Are you going to call Mrs. Zhao?

27:29.600 --> 27:30.920
Won't she think

27:31.270 --> 27:33.000
there's something between us?

27:35.080 --> 27:36.610
Then you should go back now.

27:37.080 --> 27:38.470
Just tell her...

27:38.840 --> 27:40.230
Tell her that...

27:40.490 --> 27:41.640
I'm only staying here

27:41.640 --> 27:43.030
to use your Wi-Fi.

27:43.270 --> 27:45.130
Do you think she'll believe that?

27:45.360 --> 27:46.360
What do you think?

27:46.750 --> 27:48.120
I think

27:48.580 --> 27:50.610
she'll believe whatever you say.

27:56.680 --> 27:58.290
Say it exactly as I told you.

28:18.510 --> 28:19.640
Did Mrs. Zhao agree?

28:41.230 --> 28:42.560
Don't you want to try it?

28:50.920 --> 28:51.950
Why is it sweet?

28:57.310 --> 28:59.030
Not all coffee is bitter.

29:04.320 --> 29:06.250
I won't let you have bitter things.

29:30.920 --> 29:32.180
Is your coffee bitter?

29:32.220 --> 29:33.080
Let me taste it.

29:42.360 --> 29:43.360
It's too bitter.

30:35.800 --> 30:37.260
How do you want to taste it?

31:02.370 --> 31:03.300
Perhaps...

31:08.190 --> 31:08.840
like this?

31:38.850 --> 31:39.850
It's strange.

31:40.740 --> 31:41.800
We used to be apart for so long,

31:41.800 --> 31:43.530
but I never felt this strongly.

31:44.600 --> 31:45.560
But now,

31:46.350 --> 31:47.830
even though I just saw him,

31:48.880 --> 31:50.920
I can't help thinking about him,

31:51.800 --> 31:54.080
as if we've been apart for ages.

31:59.880 --> 32:02.040
Zhao, Zhao.

32:56.180 --> 32:58.350
Why are you here so late?

32:58.710 --> 33:00.600
Didn't you say you don't know
how to redeem your card game points?

33:00.600 --> 33:01.400
I came to help.

33:02.530 --> 33:03.090
Right.

33:03.430 --> 33:04.990
My phone is out of battery.

33:05.420 --> 33:07.080
It's okay. Let it charge for a while.

33:07.080 --> 33:07.940
Just wait here.

33:30.810 --> 33:32.610
You came specifically to see me?

33:37.030 --> 33:37.840
What else?

33:44.900 --> 33:45.590
By the way,

33:45.900 --> 33:48.430
what did that real estate agent
want with you?

33:48.920 --> 33:50.520
I'm going to sell the garage.

33:50.610 --> 33:51.440
Sell?

33:52.670 --> 33:55.070
You're not going
to run the garage anymore?

33:56.510 --> 33:57.570
I'll run it for now.

33:57.840 --> 33:58.880
Until when?

33:59.670 --> 34:00.670
One month at most.

34:03.160 --> 34:05.360
Are you sure you want to talk about this?

34:07.790 --> 34:09.389
Didn't you say you missed me?

34:12.460 --> 34:14.020
When did I say I missed you?

34:16.110 --> 34:18.440
Then why did you
call my name so many times?

34:22.360 --> 34:23.239
I did not.

34:25.760 --> 34:26.840
Well, I missed you.

35:03.590 --> 35:04.400
Jin Zhao.

35:06.060 --> 35:06.860
Where are you?

35:14.620 --> 35:15.180
Coming.

35:25.820 --> 35:28.350
You can exchange these points
for 5 kg of rice.

35:28.850 --> 35:29.980
Impressive, right?

35:31.710 --> 35:33.870
It took me several months,

35:34.840 --> 35:37.100
and they only let me play
five times a day.

35:38.170 --> 35:39.770
First place gets 200 grains.

35:40.590 --> 35:41.430
Mu,

35:41.990 --> 35:43.680
the turtle hasn't been fed today.

35:43.680 --> 35:45.010
Could you feed it for me?

35:48.950 --> 35:50.550
First place gets 200 grains,

35:50.680 --> 35:52.280
second place gets 100,

35:52.760 --> 35:54.090
and third place gets 50.

35:54.630 --> 35:56.630
Only when you save up 10,000 grains,

35:56.720 --> 35:58.840
can you exchange them for 5 kg of rice.

36:00.390 --> 36:01.590
You need rice at home?

36:02.680 --> 36:05.280
This thing sparked my competitiveness.

36:06.510 --> 36:07.970
You're quite persistent.

36:08.360 --> 36:10.020
Let me write down the address.

36:10.280 --> 36:12.920
If they didn't limit me
to five games a day,

36:14.280 --> 36:15.880
I could have redeemed

36:16.200 --> 36:17.280
15 kg.

36:19.070 --> 36:20.390
Or even 20 kg by now.

36:22.060 --> 36:24.110
All done. Just wait for the rice at home.

36:24.110 --> 36:25.510
-All done?
-I'm leaving.

36:25.630 --> 36:26.360
I'm leaving.

36:26.920 --> 36:28.790
Come back for a meal when you have time.

36:28.790 --> 36:31.870
I've come up
with some new dishes recently.

36:32.590 --> 36:34.650
You can also try the rice I exchanged.

36:35.070 --> 36:36.600
Sure, when I finish my work.

36:38.430 --> 36:39.230
I'm going, Mu.

36:43.350 --> 36:45.020
I'll earn another 5 kg.

37:08.390 --> 37:09.390
Go to the balcony.

37:19.830 --> 37:20.630
Zhao!

37:35.600 --> 37:37.200
I want to show you something.

37:59.690 --> 38:03.050
♪ What was it that brought me to you? ♪

38:03.440 --> 38:05.350
♪ Perhaps it was fate's design ♪

38:05.920 --> 38:09.660
♪ Through all our winding paths,
we always find each other ♪

38:09.680 --> 38:13.280
♪ The storm turned to rain,
and everything was swept away ♪

38:13.310 --> 38:15.020
♪ Slowly, everything becomes clear ♪

38:15.040 --> 38:17.400
♪ In your gaze ♪

38:17.690 --> 38:19.650
♪ I found the answer ♪

38:19.680 --> 38:21.720
♪ There's a feeling so strong ♪

38:21.760 --> 38:24.880
♪ Our story is still unfolding ♪

38:23.280 --> 38:23.880
Zhao.

38:24.470 --> 38:25.360
I want to see this.

38:25.020 --> 38:28.930
♪ Waiting for the perfect ending ♪

38:25.590 --> 38:26.920
You need to come with me.

38:30.640 --> 38:33.090
♪ It all began the moment I met you ♪

38:31.070 --> 38:31.680
Okay.

38:33.110 --> 38:35.580
♪ There's a pull I cannot explain ♪

38:33.360 --> 38:34.200
I promise you.

38:35.240 --> 38:36.240
I'll definitely go with you.

38:35.610 --> 38:38.730
♪ My eyes follow you,
my heart chases after you ♪

38:38.750 --> 38:40.560
♪ I just can't help it ♪

38:40.580 --> 38:43.030
♪ When I gaze across the sky ♪

38:43.060 --> 38:45.560
♪ Not even miles can keep us apart ♪

38:45.580 --> 38:48.590
♪ Sweet longing drifts on the wind ♪

38:48.610 --> 38:50.830
♪ I can feel you near ♪

38:51.150 --> 38:53.580
♪ Feel you're with me ♪

38:53.600 --> 38:55.900
♪ Forget the sunsets, forget the tides ♪

38:56.080 --> 38:58.140
♪ Watch the years pass
and wander the world ♪

38:58.490 --> 39:00.170
♪ You're the only one in my heart ♪

39:00.190 --> 39:02.860
